Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽乃呢  還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎  沒嘉賓根本撐不了兩小時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記一切去唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為弄到票了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去了  所以這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺小姐似乎想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為約好了…的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多得厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…都是由綺的歌迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常感謝他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…高興程度是99%吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只有冬彌君來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙和彰君  美笑也都送了票
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是在為我們著想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不需要在乎那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merry  Christmas  冬彌君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me…Merry…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  立刻就去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君也快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡解禁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺小姐  趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們也走吧  沒人會來這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後開始真的要忙了  我們都是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你周圍的所有人都是你的對手…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立場…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是在說由綺的轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為由綺會原諒你的花心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她不能原諒自己是花心的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然說起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了  還有另一個對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎連歌神都被由綺迷住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我和理奈只是為贏他  而走到現在的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌是奴隸  是道具  他必須臣服於我們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我或許是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺卻不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被允許侍奉他  被他擺弄被他斥責
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與他一起嬉戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾挑起戰爭  然後擊敗他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白嗎  今天的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想唱歌  連一秒都不能停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有歌聲陪伴的話  不唱歌的話就會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺不就是歌的戀人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  這是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不唱歌也不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是觀眾卻得到了這樣的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是  青年  你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓所有聽到歌聲的人感受到這種錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是職業歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是森川由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年  你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是對手是我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會有點怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊  找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冬彌那裏…是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君他去演唱會了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了吧  或許是去喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君的爸爸怎麼會一個人去那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在家的話去了也沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是拜訪人家的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經說過會去拜訪了  對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳已經好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能推動車了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多虧了你  非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對冬彌沒有這麼客氣過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七瀨君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌稱呼你是用名字的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後也請你多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一場雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  時間…去演唱會的話也是理所當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候就在這等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:17:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼時候  剛剛來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有等你  只是剛好到了附近的朋友家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起你簡歷上的地址是這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友不在家  當然是女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和男朋友去約會了  因為是平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就來看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  不好意思  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道現在幾點嗎  我家人會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  本來是想送給朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在  所以就送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕就不需要了吧  你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能讓手這麼冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉這麼冷的女孩子回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷得我都流眼淚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會打什麼主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:18:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為做這種事我就會感動  什麼都原諒你對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以期待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了  我才不會給你什麼  汗倒是一大把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  我想你還是稍微減一下量比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減…說減肥啦  而且根本不需要減
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是由綺？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這位是由綺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺…小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀比藤井大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我聽說是同年的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？同年？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的票
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步的話我才不去  這種鬼天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一首歌終於看到了大熱的前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由松山芽乃小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  你沒事吧  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把傘…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麻奈忘了帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼麻奈會去冬彌的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌  你爸爸他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.52,0:24:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的空白頁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.99,0:24:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有填滿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.26,0:24:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

